Craig ZwerlingVice President of Finance
Craig Zwerling has over eight years of experience in healthcare corporate finance. Prior to joining iAnthus Capital Management, LLC, Mr. Zwerling was the Director, Corporate and Project Finance and Reimbursement for ProCure Treatment Centers. Prior to joining ProCure, Mr. Zwerling worked at Citi as a Financial Analyst in the healthcare investment banking group. Mr. Zwerling graduated magna cum laude and earned a B.S. in Business Management from Babson College, with a concentration in Finance.
 









Ms. Radovan worked at J.P. Morgan as a Financial Analyst in the not-for-profit healthcare investment banking group.  She graduated with honors from the University of Chicago with a B.A. in Economics.


